"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-08-05-paris-olympics-jess-fox-misses-kayak-cross-medal-104182642\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  Sport  Topic:Olympic Games  Elena Lilik from Germany, Jessica Fox from Australia and Viktoria Wolffhardt from Austria during the cross event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"score\": 0.9999961026595433, \"rank\": 3.892285314332627e-06, \"text\": \"Elena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\"}, {\"begin\": 218, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9823321648679271, \"rank\": 0.009688925100227312, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"score\": 0.548202986974713, \"rank\": 0.8241415192508661, \"text\": \"Jessica Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999947830142107, \"rank\": 2.6214072900330986e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktoria_Wolffhardt\", \"score\": 0.9999995721592319, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Viktoria Wolffhardt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktoria_Wolffhardt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Viktoria_Wolffhardt\"}, {\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9986952996834695, \"rank\": 0.0013048799294026556, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Sebastian Kahnert/picture alliance)  Jessica Fox's quest for an historic third Olympic medal in Paris is over with her sister Noemie eliminating the superstar in their kayak cross round.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"score\": 0.9993412536292332, \"rank\": 0.0004668008407330083, \"text\": \"Sebastian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"score\": 0.548202986974713, \"rank\": 0.8241415192508661, \"text\": \"Jessica Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.178014577097586e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwinning the C1 and K1 titles, Fox was attempting a golden treble with the new Olympic event added to the Paris schedule.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lega_Pro_Prima_Divisione\", \"score\": 0.9757074935112353, \"rank\": 0.02429607916542336, \"text\": \"C1\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lega_Pro_Prima_Divisione\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lega_Pro_Prima_Divisione\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"score\": 0.9999996752067618, \"rank\": 2.7779668159121295e-07, \"text\": \"K1\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\"}, {\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9984516015778767, \"rank\": 0.00091638191350398, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.178014577097586e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But her plans came unstuck on Sunday night (AEST) when a costly gate error meant she failed to make the top two to advance to the quarter-finals, finishing last.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just did not pull out my best race,\\\" said the 30-year-old, who owns six Olympic medals, including three gold from her four Games.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was tough off the start, I got really tangled, and I was trying to chase.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I turned fourth, and climbed up one spot, and almost pulled off the overtake at the last gate.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's kayak cross, and you can have a plan, but nothing goes to plan.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999995836015799, \"rank\": 4.163984914566578e-07, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie Fox leads the field during a kayak cross heat.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999995836015799, \"rank\": 4.163984914566578e-07, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie is still in with a shot of a medal.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Justin Setterfield)  \\\"I am gutted, but at the same time, when you see your little sister (Noemie) win the heat, I was really proud of her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Fox siblings were drawn in the same four-paddler heat, against veteran Spaniard and three-time Olympic medallist Maialen Chourraut, and Dutch paddler Martina Wegman.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9984516015778767, \"rank\": 0.00091638191350398, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9349598447978883, \"rank\": 0.054456960969849665, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maialen_Chourraut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maialen Chourraut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maialen_Chourraut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maialen_Chourraut\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9619733434515145, \"rank\": 0.03827142736525654, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martina_Wegman\", \"score\": 0.999999077835098, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Martina Wegman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martina_Wegman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martina_Wegman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noemie, 27, got off to a flying start, storming clear with her sister at the back of the field.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jessica went past Wegman but as she attempted to claw ahead of Chourraut she missed a gate and had to paddle back around which ruled her out of the running.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9967908189467645, \"rank\": 0.0019674531554613986, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After crossing the line the elder Fox immediately embraced Noemie, who is making her Olympics debut.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9984516015778767, \"rank\": 0.00091638191350398, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, Tim Anderson won his heat to book his quarter-final berth in the men's event while Tristan Carter also advanced after finishing second.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Anderson_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.5371864811784893, \"rank\": 0.4542996214169507, \"text\": \"Tim Anderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Anderson_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Anderson_(baseball)\"}, {\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9999572241517464, \"rank\": 3.3726793017634506e-05, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}, {\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.999996049193288, \"rank\": 3.877334286261888e-06, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jessica said while there was disappointed there was also relief after wrapping up a monster campaign in France, that also included being one of Australia's flag-bearers at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9967908189467645, \"rank\": 0.0019674531554613986, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5502933230657856, \"rank\": 0.8069649432571405, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999947830142107, \"rank\": 2.6214072900330986e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is also some relief in finishing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is partly disappointment to not progress and to not try and have a crack at that third medal but there is pride, relief and exhaustion from the last week of competing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AAP  Topic:Cricket  Topic:Cricket  Topic:Courts  Topic:NRL  Topic:NRL  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Social Media  Topic:Federal Government  Topic:War  Topic:Royalty  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Royalty  Topic:War  Canoeing and Kayaking  France  Olympic Games  Sport  Topic:Domestic Violence  Topic:Social Media  Topic:Federal Government  Topic:War  Topic:Royalty  Topic:Rural and Remote Communities  Topic:Pollution  Topic:Geography  Topic:Royalty  We acknowledge Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples as the First Australians and Traditional Custodians of the lands where we live, learn, and work.\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 3152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"score\": 0.9994126992335223, \"rank\": 0.00038194739241699955, \"text\": \"NRL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2607, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"score\": 0.9994126992335223, \"rank\": 0.00038194739241699955, \"text\": \"NRL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rugby_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2773, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0,